## Group Drivers

### List all drivers [GET /drivers]
Returns all available deliveries.

+ Request (application/json)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (array[Driver])

### Invite a driver [POST /drivers]
Creates driver.

+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes
      + Include User

+ Response 200 (application/json)
